name: hugo_website
description: ## Setup add hugo.toml file with the publishDir and hugo_cache you want to use  ```toml baseURL = 'https://hugo.ropelab.uber.space/' languageCode = 'de' title = 'Social Rope Lab' # hugo_cache = '/home/ropelab/tmp' # publishDir = '/var/www/virtual/ropelab/hugo.ropelab.uber.space' hugo_cache = './tmp' publishDir = './result' ```
